Ex-President Hosni Mubarak Plans to Apologize to Egyptians, Arabiya Says

-- B y   Z a i d   S a b a h   A b d   A l h a m i d
-- 
2011-05-17T00:22:11Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-17/ex-president-hosni-mubarak-plans-to-apologize-to-egyptians-arabiya-says.html
Former Egyptian President  Hosni
Mubarak  plans to apologize to citizens in a speech, Al Arabiya
television reported, citing the Al Shorouk newspaper.   Mubarak may also say that he and his wife will relinquish
all their property, Arabiya said. The speech is still being
written and Mubarak may record it for local television,
according to the report.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Zaid Sabah Abd Alhamid in Washington at 
 zalhamid@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Vivek Shankar at 
 vshankar3@bloomberg.net  